				\begin{document}$$\,S_{w} \,\,\,{\text{and}}\,\,{\text{M}}$$\end{document} increases this distribution. Meanwhile, the increase of the parameters α,δ,λ2andSc\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
