				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\alpha ,\,\delta ,\,\lambda_{2} \,\,\,{\text{and}}\,\,{\text{S}}_{{\text{c}}}$$\end{document} decreases it.
The skin friction, Nusselt and Sherwood numerals are illustrated graphically with the variation of the relevant parameters.
